data.text: On 1th April, day with highest average dwell times, the average dwell times were highest between 1 - 30 April, which peaked at 124 mins.
On 23th April, day with lowest average dwell times, the average dwell times were highest between 1 - 30 April, which peaked at 1 mins.
NTUC Fairprice has the highest average dwell time of 30.2 mins, with dwellers most commonly visiting from 10AM-12PM.
KFC has the lowest average dwell time of 4.2 mins, with dwellers mostly visiting from 10AM-12PM.

data.text: In April 02017, 50% of patrons were families, 20% were young couples, and delivery riders, white collared workers, and Persona 5 made up 10% of the patrons each.
The multi-line graph shows the trend of patrons based on their age over time in April, 2017.

The highest number of patrons from a single age group was on 27rd April with 3900 from the Elderly age group. The lowest number of patrons from a single age group was on 8rd April with 50 from the Young Adults age group.
